{"title":"Bloqueo AV 2-1 Causas iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Bloqueo AV 2-1 Causas iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Bloqueo AV 2:1 —\\NCausas y Enfoque","guid":"ECDzaoP7fupNGTBmlBFL-Q","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Concepto\\NClave","guid":"IQHWOeai04SgdbBRg1su8Q","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Conduccion AV alternante → 1 P conducida, 1 P bloqueada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"NO SE PUEDE CLASIFICAR como Mobitz I o II con un solo trazo ECG","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Puede ser NODAL o INFRANODAL → pronostico y manejo distintos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Prevalencia ~2% en Holter poblacion general","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"0","text":"Clasificacion\\NElectrocardiografica","guid":"OhZmDXxcDxLj2bLds893dw","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Bloqueo NODAL\\N(suprahisiano)","guid":"CMo31CyQ2s6xrtuW5zSHiw","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"QRS angosto (<120 ms) → sugiere nivel nodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"PR del latido conducido generalmente prolongado (>200 ms)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"Responde a ATROPINA (acorta PR, mejora conduccion)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"7","text":"Empeora con masaje carotideo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"Frecuencia ventricular relativamente preservada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"7","text":"PRONOSTICO generalmente benigno si causa reversible","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"6","text":"Bloqueo INFRANODAL\\N(hisiano o infrahisiano)","guid":"-2uNE4DF_go_4FItuN61nA","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"QRS ancho (>=120 ms con BRD o BRI) → ALERTA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"PR del latido conducido puede ser normal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"NO responde a atropina → puede EMPEORAR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"Mejora con isoproterenol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"14","text":"RIESGO de progresion a BAV completo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"14","text":"INDICACION de marcapasos (Clase I ACC/AHA 2018)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"6","text":"Herramientas\\Npara diferenciar","guid":"XtKWYOdKgBfAM3zUHIViKA","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Maniobras vagales → empeoran nodal, mejoran infranodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"Ejercicio/atropina → mejoran nodal, empeoran infranodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Estudio electrofisiologico → intervalo AH vs HV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Holter 24h → buscar periodos de Wenckebach (sugiere nodal)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"Causas Degenerativas\\N(MAS FRECUENTE EN AM)","guid":"MDCK5hgp8EE8BYPDGb-PqA","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Enfermedad\\Nde Lenegre","guid":"cJc3HFRBsZFzWgmUHLCxTg","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Fibrosis idiopatica del sistema His-Purkinje","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"Progresiva → asociada a envejecimiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"Causa mas comun de BAV en >65 anos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"27","text":"Puede asociar bloqueo de rama previo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"26","text":"Enfermedad\\Nde Lev","guid":"NMvaBYX5HP6MBFtlD-EmAg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Calcificacion del esqueleto fibroso cardiaco","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Extension a sistema de conduccion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"Asociada a estenosis aortica calcificada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"Frecuente en AM con cardiopatia estructural","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"26","text":"Fibrosis senil del\\Nsistema de conduccion","guid":"b7EOAJ-o_ITI9JjjRba0MA","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Degeneracion progresiva relacionada con edad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Prevalencia aumenta exponencialmente >70 anos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"0","text":"Causas Isquemicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"IAM INFERIOR\\N(territorio ACD)","guid":"F2ln_YdtzTWw5PcyRsAhcw","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Bloqueo generalmente NODAL (suprahisiano)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Transitorio en 90% de los casos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Resuelve en 5-7 dias habitualmente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"Arteria del nodo AV → rama de ACD (85%) o Cx (15%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"41","text":"Manejo conservador inicial (atropina si sintomatico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"41","text":"Marcapasos transitorio solo si inestabilidad hemodinamica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"40","text":"IAM ANTERIOR\\N(territorio DA)","guid":"Y6fyTpJ291yHBYN2_xrv2g","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Bloqueo generalmente INFRANODAL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"MAYOR mortalidad (OR ~5) vs IAM inferior","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"Implica necrosis extensa del septum","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"Indicacion de marcapasos DEFINITIVO frecuente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"48","text":"Progresion a BAV completo mas probable","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"40","text":"Isquemia\\Ncronica","guid":"HvMnjhT2-x6IebvZ2gnOuw","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Fibrosis post-infarto del sistema de conduccion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"Miocardiopatia isquemica avanzada","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"Causas Farmacologicas\\N(REVERSIBLE → BUSCAR\\NSIEMPRE)","guid":"_6jKELUCy3HMNmmyDGTexg","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Betabloqueadores","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Atenolol, metoprolol, bisoprolol, carvedilol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Efecto cronotropico y dromotropico negativo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"MAS COMUN en combinacion con otros farmacos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"58","text":"AM → mayor susceptibilidad por reserva cronotropica reducida","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"57","text":"Calcioantagonistas\\Nno-dihidropiridinicos","guid":"qG23PsSYu9S2jy8GFlh6dA","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"Verapamilo → MAYOR efecto sobre nodo AV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"Diltiazem","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"63","text":"Combinacion con betabloqueadores → SINERGISMO PELIGROSO","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"57","text":"Digoxina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Efecto vagotonico directo sobre nodo AV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Toxicidad → rango terapeutico estrecho en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Insuficiencia renal → acumulacion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"Nivel serico >1.2 ng/mL aumenta riesgo en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"67","text":"Antidoto: anticuerpos antidigoxina (Fab)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"57","text":"Antiarritmicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"Clase IC (flecainida, propafenona) → bloqueo infranodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"Clase III (amiodarona, sotalol) → bloqueo nodal e infranodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"Amiodarona → efecto acumulativo, vida media larga (~40 dias)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"Clase IA (procainamida) → bloqueo His-Purkinje","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"57","text":"Otros farmacos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"Litio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"Clonidina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"Donepezilo y anticolinesterasicos → PERLA GERIATRICA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"78","text":"Ivabradina (sinergismo con betabloqueadores)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"78","text":"Cannabinoides","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"0","text":"Causas Inflamatorias e\\NInfiltrativas","guid":"oVmnqsRKpN4q4moGvuHwdw","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Sarcoidosis\\Ncardiaca","guid":"0DODSO7V19i2i0TMrlwg2w","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"5-10% de sarcoidosis sistemica → afectacion cardiaca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"BAV como PRESENTACION INICIAL en ~25% de casos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"RMN cardiaca → realce tardio con gadolinio (patron NO isquemico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"PET-FDG → captacion activa miocardica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"Corticoides → pueden revertir bloqueo si inflamacion activa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"85","text":"Requiere marcapasos + tratamiento inmunosupresor","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"84","text":"Amiloidosis\\Ncardiaca","guid":"IOXs0hg1bx88IZ1zwoz5Sw","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Tipo AL (cadenas ligeras) y ATTR (transtiretina)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"ATTR senil → FRECUENTE en AM >80 anos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"Engrosamiento septal + bajo voltaje en ECG → CLAVE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"92","text":"Centellograma con pirofosfato Tc99 → screening ATTR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"92","text":"BAV por infiltracion del sistema de conduccion","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"84","text":"Miocarditis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"Viral (Coxsackie, adenovirus, SARS-CoV-2)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"Autoinmune (LES, artritis reumatoide)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"98","text":"Celulas gigantes → BAV frecuente, mal pronostico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"98","text":"Generalmente transitorio si viral","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"0","text":"Causas\\NInfecciosas","guid":"SMzakNdVG-6VA8M9dYDHWg","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Enfermedad\\Nde Chagas","guid":"MLzE-Y4Dd5aqoCBlTIqphg","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"Trypanosoma cruzi → tropismo por sistema de conduccion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"BRD + HBAI → patron tipico (Chagas cronico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"Endemia en Chile (regiones norte y centro)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"104","text":"BAV puede ser primera manifestacion cardiaca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"104","text":"Solicitar serologia en pacientes de zonas endemicas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"103","text":"Enfermedad\\Nde Lyme","guid":"_HxYCVclnCU9YbSDkrtGYw","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Borrelia burgdorferi → nodo AV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"BAV generalmente reversible con antibioticos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"110","text":"Ceftriaxona IV si BAV 2do o 3er grado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"110","text":"Marcapasos transitorio, NO definitivo (resuelve)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"103","text":"Endocarditis\\Ninfecciosa","guid":"REne95h4N8rBoaqMjuuP0Q","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"Extension perivalvular → absceso septal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"Bloqueo AV como signo de complicacion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"Valvula aortica → proximidad al His","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"0","text":"Causas Postquirurgicas\\Ny Postintervencion","guid":"G-qlMbLlJO9uBjaAZ3GvTQ","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"TAVI (reemplazo valvular\\Naortico transcateter)","guid":"oGQtoW8ccRmL4aew6C7MYg","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"Incidencia BAV nuevo ~15-20% (varia segun protesis)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"Mas frecuente con CoreValve vs Edwards SAPIEN","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"BRI nuevo post-TAVI → monitorizar progresion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"120","text":"Puede requerir marcapasos definitivo en ~10-15%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"119","text":"Cirugia valvular\\Nconvencional","guid":"DBX8qALOP6Du_U5r_7j90g","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"Cirugia valvula aortica y mitral → proximidad al His","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"Causa principal de BAV en <55 anos (Mkoko 2022)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"Puede ser transitorio (edema) o definitivo (danio)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"119","text":"Ablacion\\Npor cateter","guid":"n9W5SpmA17AIgWBZzoTBtA","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"Ablacion de nodo AV (intencional)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"Ablacion de vias accesorias septales → riesgo BAV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"Ablacion de FA → dano colateral nodal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"119","text":"Cierre de CIV → lesion His por proximidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"0","text":"Causas\\NCongenitas","guid":"hGnaewprvMgMCsYNgLfF3Q","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"Lupus neonatal (anticuerpos\\Nanti-Ro/anti-La maternos)","guid":"UDC1FfznWCKD6OyvTWrfMw","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"BAV generalmente 3er grado pero 2:1 descrito","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"Deteccion prenatal por ecografia fetal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"Dexametasona transplacentaria → controversial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"135","text":"Frecuente indicacion de marcapasos postnatal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"134","text":"BAV congenito\\Naislado","guid":"0qDg0mou1_tRGKpr5ZD61A","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"Asociado a cardiopatias congenitas (TGA corregida, CIV)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"Mutaciones geneticas (NKX2-5, LMNA, SCN5A)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"0","text":"Causas\\NMetabolicas y\\NElectroliticas","guid":"hb8_6qjOcKUvJ1QbSGNEjQ","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"Hiperkalemia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"K+ >6.5 mEq/L → prolongacion PR, BAV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"K+ >7.0 mEq/L → riesgo BAV completo y asistolia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"Primer signo ECG: ondas T picudas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"144","text":"Progresion: T picuda → PR largo → QRS ancho → BAV → FV/asistolia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"144","text":"EMERGENCIA → gluconato de calcio + insulina/glucosa + salbutamol","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"143","text":"Hipermagnesemia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"Frecuente en ERC con uso de antiacidos/laxantes con Mg","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"143","text":"Hipotiroidismo severo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Mixedema → bradicardia sinusal + BAV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"Reversible con levotiroxina","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"143","text":"Hipotermia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"Bradicardia progresiva proporcional a temperatura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"Onda J de Osborn en ECG","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"0","text":"Causa Funcional/Vagotonica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"Tono vagal aumentado","guid":"","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Deportistas → hipertonia vagal fisiologica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"Nocturno → BAV 2:1 transitorio durante sueno (BENIGNO)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"Sincope vasovagal → componente cardioinhibitorio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"158","text":"Reflejo Bezold-Jarisch (IAM inferior)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"158","text":"Responde a atropina → confirma mecanismo vagal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"0","text":"Enfoque\\NDiagnostico","guid":"Ah6qEJU-1lWW6NaPIZ6jLw","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"Paso 1 → ECG 12 derivaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"Ancho del QRS → nodal vs infranodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"Morfologia del PR conducido","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"Evidencia de IAM, BRD/BRI previo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"165","text":"Paso 2 → Maniobras farmacologicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"Atropina 0.5-1 mg IV → mejora nodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"Si empeora o no responde → INFRANODAL","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"165","text":"Paso 3 → Holter 24-48h","guid":"","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Buscar periodos de Wenckebach intercalados (nodal)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Correlacionar con sintomas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"BAV nocturno aislado → probable vagotonico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"165","text":"Paso 4 → Laboratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"Electrolitos (K+, Mg2+, Ca2+)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"TSH, T4 libre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"177","text":"Digoxinemia si aplica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"177","text":"Serologia Chagas si zona endemica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"177","text":"Troponinas si sospecha isquemica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"165","text":"Paso 5 → Imagenes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"Ecocardiograma → funcion ventricular, valvulopatia, infiltracion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"RMN cardiaca → sarcoidosis, miocarditis, fibrosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"183","text":"Centellograma pirofosfato → amiloidosis ATTR","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"165","text":"Paso 6 → Estudio electrofisiologico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"Intervalo AH prolongado → bloqueo nodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"Intervalo HV prolongado (>70 ms) → bloqueo infranodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"Indicado si diagnostico no claro y decision de marcapasos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"0","text":"Indicaciones de Marcapasos\\N(ACC/AHA 2018)","guid":"f1w6KEcIf_BAkwUfAFeq6A","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"Clase I\\N(indicacion\\Ndefinitiva)","guid":"5feDZSsL59MWEoZf_SLzaw","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"BAV 2do grado con sintomas atribuibles","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"BAV 2:1 infranodal (QRS ancho)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"192","text":"BAV en contexto de enfermedades neuromusculares","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"191","text":"Clase IIa","guid":"","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"BAV 2:1 asintomatico con QRS ancho","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"BAV asociado a sarcoidosis cardiaca","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"199","parent":"191","text":"Clase III\\N(NO\\Nmarcapasos)","guid":"lcqJkJ4ZE98cS_4XyNXC4Q","children":[{"id":"200","parent":"199","text":"BAV transitorio por causa reversible (farmacos, isquemia aguda)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"199","text":"BAV vagotonico nocturno en jovenes asintomaticos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriatricas","guid":"fEU0HsMV7kxMJ5Hq5aI1oA","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"Degeneracion del sistema de conduccion → CAUSA MAS FRECUENTE >75a","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"Polifarmacia → siempre descartar causa farmacologica primero","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"Deprescripcion como intervencion terapeutica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"Fragilidad → considerar riesgo/beneficio del marcapasos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"TAVI → creciente prevalencia de BAV post-procedimiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"202","text":"Amiloidosis ATTR senil → causa emergente subestimada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"202","text":"Donepezilo/anticolinesterasicos → causa oculta de bradicardia en demencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"202","text":"Sincope + BAV en AM → alta morbimortalidad por caidas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClinicas","guid":"jRlP16v1BneOG1HlHSBL4Q","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"BAV 2:1 NO es sinonimo de Mobitz II → puede ser nodal o infranodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"QRS ancho + BAV 2:1 = INFRANODAL hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"SIEMPRE revisar farmacos antes de etiquetar como degenerativo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"211","text":"Donepezilo puede causar BAV en pacientes con demencia → PERLA GERIATRICA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"211","text":"Amiloidosis ATTR → pensar en todo AM >80a con HVI + bajo voltaje + BAV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"211","text":"Sarcoidosis → RMN cardiaca si BAV en <60a sin causa clara","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"211","text":"Chagas → pedir serologia en pacientes de zonas endemicas chilenas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"211","text":"BAV post-TAVI → complicacion frecuente, monitorizar BRI nuevo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"211","text":"Atropina que EMPEORA el bloqueo → confirma localizacion infranodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"211","text":"Nocturno + asintomatico + deportista = BENIGNO, no requiere marcapasos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"0","text":"VER\\NTAMBIEN","guid":"oPqj5l7KZ-fGUNB9cRuvZg","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"→ Farmacologia Cardiovascular en AM (Cardiogeriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"→ Sincope en Adulto Mayor (Geriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"→ Estenosis Aortica y TAVI (Cardiogeriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"222","text":"→ Amiloidosis Cardiaca (Cardiogeriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"222","text":"→ Enfermedad de Chagas (Infectologia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"222","text":"→ Hiperkalemia en Urgencia (Medicina Critica)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"1. Barold SS, Hayes DL. Second-degree atrioventricular block: a reappraisal. Mayo Clin Proc. 2001;76(1):44-57.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"2. Kusumoto FM et al. 2018 ACC/AHA/HRS Guideline on Evaluation and Management of Patients With Bradycardia and Cardiac Conduction Delay. Circulation. 2019;140(8):e382-e482.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"229","text":"3. Mkoko P et al. Causes of Heart Block in Young and Middle-Aged South Africans. Curr Probl Cardiol. 2022;48(8):101247.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"229","text":"4. Barold SS, Herweg B. The effect of hyperkalaemia on cardiac rhythm devices. Europace. 2014;16(4):467-76.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"229","text":"5. Brignole M et al. 2021 ESC Guidelines on cardiac pacing and cardiac resynchronization therapy. Eur Heart J. 2021;42(35):3427-3520.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"229","text":"6. Rubin GA, Passeri JJ. Cardiac Sarcoidosis: Diagnosis and Management. Curr Cardiol Rep. 2023;25(8):911-920.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"229","text":"7. Gillmore JD et al. Nonbiopsy Diagnosis of Cardiac Transthyretin Amyloidosis. Circulation. 2016;133(24):2404-12.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":236,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Bloqueo AV 2-1 Causas iPad","id":"map_702","resolved_references":[]}